name: King Dog Inu
description: "King Dog Inu is a project based on the Binance Smart Chain blockchain. He was born to be the king of the dog land in blockchain technology. Our goal is to enable something as complex as dog adoption to be made available to everyone by harnessing the power of NFT and blockchain. King Dog Inu is a community-driven charity Token. Our end goal? Join forces with all King Dog Inu communities far and wide for a glorious trip to the moon together!"
